             * - `{{ language }}` — The document language code (e.g., "eng", "deu").
             *
             * @var ?string
             */
            public readonly ?string $vlmPrompt = null,
            /**
             * Hardware acceleration for ONNX Runtime models (e.g. PaddleOCR, layout detection).
